rve scatter and smoothness. Candidate variables\nare selected as having variability index values significantly higher than\nexpected for objects of similar brightness in the given set of observations.\nThe Hubble Catalog of Variables will be released in 2018.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2017 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Jul 2017 09:52:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-13"}
